[**90% staked!**](https://opensea.io/collection/staked-critterz) ** 2650 unique owners + renters.** The first fully on-chain NFT collection to enable P2E while playing Minecraft. Stake to generate $BLOCK tokens in-game and use $BLOCK tokens to claim [Plots of in-game land as NFTs](https://opensea.io/collection/critterzplots). Join us on Minecraft at: **mc.critterz.xyz**

We solved a lot of engineering challenges to bring Critterz to life, including a custom oracle, gas saving mechanics, and renting mechanisms. You can learn more here: https://www.critterz.xyz/whitepaper
